--- 
title  : Lime
suite  : RubyWorks
summary: Gherkin-style Test Framework
authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Lime is a pure Ruby variation of Cucumber's Gherkin
  BDD test system that runs on top of the Ruby
  Universal Test Harness.

